<i>noun</i>: 타개책 [타ː개책], 치료법 [치료뻡], 처방 [처ː방], 요법 [요뻡], 묘약 [묘ː약] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>타개책 [타ː개책]</dt><br>
<dd>breakthrough; solution; remedy</dd><br>
<dd>어려운 일을 잘 처리하여 해결할 방법.</dd><br>
<dd>A method to resolve a difficult problem and find a solution.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>치료법 [치료뻡]</dt><br>
<dd>cure; treatment; remedy</dd><br>
<dd>병이나 상처를 낫게 하는 방법.</dd><br>
<dd>A method of treating a disease or wound.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>처방 [처ː방]</dt><br>
<dd>1. prescription</dd><br>
<dd>병을 치료하기 위해 약을 짓는 방법.</dd><br>
<dd>A formula for preparing medication to treat an illness.</dd><br>
<dd>2. remedy</dd><br>
<dd>문제를 처리하는 방법.</dd><br>
<dd>A way to solve problems.</dd><br>
<dd>3. prescription</dd><br>
<dd>병을 치료하기 위해 약을 짓는 방법을 적은 종이.</dd><br>
<dd>Written instructions stating a formula for preparing medication to treat an illness.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>요법 [요뻡]</dt><br>
<dd>remedy; therapy; treatment</dd><br>
<dd>병을 치료하는 방법.</dd><br>
<dd>A way of treating an illness.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>묘약 [묘ː약]</dt><br>
<dd>1. magic drug; secret medicine; cure; potion</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 병을 치료하는 데 효과가 매우 좋은 약.</dd><br>
<dd>A medicine highly effective for curing a certain disease.</dd><br>
<dd>2. remedy; magic formula; cure-all</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 문제를 해결하는 데 매우 효과적인 방법.</dd><br>
<dd>A highly effective way of solving a certain problem.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>